    <text id="A0210T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>N. K. Trout provides Alfred Chapman with the details of a particular case and
                    comments upon Judge Sheffey and Judge Fultz. He also asks Chapman about the
                    claim of a soldier's widow.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1869-03-30">March 30 1869</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My dear friend</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have your letter. I regret I did not answer you as freely on the subject of
                    that suit as you desired. I now send you the statement_ I cannot think of the
                    proceeding with its surroundings without getting excited, but it is over now.
                    the deed is done. If 15<del rend="none" hand="h1"/> is a sufficient reward for such
                    unkindness-almost <unclear>undeserved</unclear>-let it be <del rend="none" hand="h1"/></p>

                <p>We have nothing astir here. I handed your letter to Judge Sheffey Judge Fultz
                    strides as stately as a Prince since the judicial robes have fallen on him--
                        <unclear>Bennette</unclear> + Ryan are inoffice under the style + name of
                    Cline + Sons. no change is observed except in the <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to <del
                        hand="h1"/></p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am as ever<lb/>Yours Truly</salute>
                    <signed/>
                    <seg type="postscript">Have you done anything for our widow's soldiers claim?
                        How is an old <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                        <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> soldier is dead intestate <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>?</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
